title: The Cambridge Drugs Killings:  Episode 85
description:
Murder, manslaughter or accident?  Kathleen McCluskey was a self styled witch and along with her husband enjoyed sex and drugs parties in Cambridge.  But then  people started to die when they were in her company.   Coincidence: or more sinister....?
